== Running urxvt in daemon mode ==

To use urxvtd, put the following in your <code>~/.xinitrc</code> or <code>~/.xsession</code> to start the daemon on login and exit on logout:

    urxvtd -q -f -o

Then you can start up <code>urxvt</code> via:

     urxvtcd -name urxvt

     
[http://thened.net/nedlog/posts/urxvtd/ from thened.net] 


